{
  "stem": "95.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "On top of it, which, in a way, was great, that factory was bombed every day by the Allied bombers, because it was a factory that was making, from coal, synthetic fuel.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the Allies didn't want-- did not want that, because the war is going to go on and they're going to win.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it was bombed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They made shelters, very good shelters, but we were not allowed to go into shelters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "If we go into shelters, they will throw us out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You had to go and escape where you go-- wherever you want to escape the bombs, but not in shelters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Sometimes, we stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Sometimes, one-- I have heard from people who were in Blechhammer-- which I don't remember that-- SS guards were in their shelters, they throw away the Jews out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They said, you cannot get a shelter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "That shelter had a bomb hit it completely and killed the SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Thank You, God, we said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But I escaped one bomb.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I don't know how I escaped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There were woods all over the-- all over the factory, and we would go in the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And thank God it wasn't stone, it was like sand or some such.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "A bomb fell, maybe-- I don't know, I can't even tell-- not far away from me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I just went down with the hole, went down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I was grasping and thinking I went down with it, and I wasn't killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But then, many, many of us, did die from the bombs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But now it's January, 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we heard rumors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I mean, we always heard rumors, real or not real, that the Allies are in North Africa, and now they're winning the war in North Africa.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "There's-- there's a-- June-- June, 1944, the-- the D-Day is there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
